com.github.seqware.queryengine.model
Class Feature

java.lang.Object
  com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl.AtomImpl<Feature>
      com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.Feature
All Implemented Interfaces:
Atom<Feature>, Buildable, Taggable, Versionable<Feature>, Serializable
public class Feature
extends AtomImpl<Feature>

Features represent a GVF (which is a more generic version of a VCF). See http://genomebiology.com/2010/11/8/R88 or better http://www.sequenceontology.org/resources/gvf.html#quick_gvf_examples We will want to tag features and version features, however we probably do not want ACL features on a Feature level since there will be many many features Immutable (but tags are not)

setAdditionalAttribute

public void setAdditionalAttribute(String name,
                                   Feature.AdditionalAttributeType value)
Sets an additional attribute not covered by GVF. It is not permitted to have an additional attribute with the same name as the instance variables (case insensitive).

Parameters:
name - Attribute name, which cannot be a GVF attribute (start, stop, pragma, etc).
value - Value of the variable to be set.
